《'''巴尔金化'''》（{{lang-en|Balkinization}}<ref name="Coyle2013">{{cite book|author=Marcia Coyle|title=The Roberts Court: The Struggle for the Constitution|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=HzgBE7xNXsMC&pg=PT425|date=7 May 2013|publisher=Simon and Schuster|isbn=978-1-4516-2753-4|pages=425–|access-date=2020-07-12|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806033207/https://books.google.com/books?id=HzgBE7xNXsMC&pg=PT425|dead-url=no}}</ref>；Balkinization blog<ref name="Luban2014">{{cite book|author=David Luban|title=Torture, Power, and Law|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ulRNBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA115|date=4 September 2014|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-1-107-05109-6|pages=115–}}</ref>）是一个专注于《[[美利坚合众国宪法|美利坚合众国宪法]]》、《[[美国宪法第一修正案|美国宪法第一修正案]]》和其他[[公民自由|公民自由]]问题的[[法律|法律]][[博客|博客]]。在[[9·11事件|9·11事件]]之后的全球[[反恐|反恐]][[战争|战争]]中，该播客对[[乔治·沃克·布什|布什]][[政府|政府]]在[[公民自由|公民自由]]问题上批评态度。有中国大陆学者认为，《巴尔金化》是“一直是[[自由派|自由派]][[法学|法学]]在[[网络|网络]]上的最大阵地”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.law.ruc.edu.cn/upic/20161209/20161209145457888.pdf|title=宗教视野下的美国宪法解释：评巴尔金的《活原旨主义》|date=2016-12-09|publisher=[[中国人民大学法学院|中国人民大学法学院]]|author=丁晓东|accessdate=2020-07-12|archive-date=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714173930/http://www.law.ruc.edu.cn/upic/20161209/20161209145457888.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《巴尔金化》由[[耶鲁法学院|耶鲁法学院]][[美国宪法|美国宪法]]和第一修正案的[[菲利普·奈特讲席教授|奈特讲席教授]]（Knight Professor）[[杰克·巴尔金|杰克·巴尔金]]（Jack Balkin）<ref>{{cite book|title=National Journal|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=bLBWAAAAYAAJ|date=December 2006|publisher=National Journal Group Incorporated|pages=57–|access-date=2020-07-12|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806032831/https://books.google.com/books?id=bLBWAAAAYAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>于2003年1月13日创建<ref>{{cite news|url=https://law.yale.edu/yls-today/news/balkinization-blog-celebrates-fifth-anniversary|title=Balkinization Blog Celebrates Fifth Anniversary|date=January 14, 2008|publisher=[[Yale_Law_School|Yale Law School]]|author=|accessdate=2020-07-12|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715201826/https://law.yale.edu/yls-today/news/balkinization-blog-celebrates-fifth-anniversary|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该博客域名为[http://balkin.blogspot.com balkin.blogspot.com] {{Wayback|url=http://balkin.blogspot.com/ |date=20030327225834 }}<ref name="O.Huq2011">{{cite book|author1=Schwarz O.|author2=Aziz Huq|title=Unchecked And Unbalanced: Presidential Power in a Time of Terror|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DqWgAm1pujEC&pg=PA267|date=10 May 2011|publisher=New Press|isbn=978-1-59558-745-9|pages=267–|access-date=2020-07-12|archive-date=2020-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721174020/https://books.google.com/books?id=DqWgAm1pujEC&pg=PA267|dead-url=no}}</ref>，截至2017年6月，它的累计[[访问量|访问量]]达1100万人次<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sitemeter.com/?a=stats&s=s15balkinization|title=Balkinization|website=SiteMeter|accessdate=2020-07-12|archive-date=2007-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927013451/http://www.sitemeter.com/?a=stats&s=s15balkinization|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

